{"tid":1652031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田區手足麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-13T14:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:10:21.000Z","uid":223399,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15115eb519058ada45318eb18856eb3900108e2d","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"今日晏晝至少有兩個絕佳嘅打狗時機<br />\n1.車公廟條馬路我哋有兩邊可以包抄佢哋<br />\n2.文禮閣往沙田方向(鐵路隔離)得幾隻狗<br />\n<br />\n重點係我哋就算人唔多都有幾十人，絕對打得贏幾隻甚至十幾隻<br />\n<br />\n有人話前線諗住退結果就全部退，但亦都有前線話打結果就無人理<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋無心理準備唔該你哋返入商場唱歌，唔好再呃我有好多人一齊衝<br />\n<br />\n但最好笑係一到夜晚啲狗有增援嗰陣就又有人想揾狗打<br />\n<br />\n沙田次次就好似夜晚夠鐘食晚飯就散咁，次次淨係可以羨慕隔離區有幾勇<br />\n然後再睇連登就係睇啲人笑沙田區垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我希望再有18區開花 沙田可以打一場漂亮嘅勝仗"},{"pid":"787939f645887e69dc9bd70a664dba90e99690f8","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"自推10就算"},{"pid":"50fd62f061a904ddab31a1fadfa67338907d27f9","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"推(1/10)"},{"pid":"ea52478af31d2131049beab60e4c3dc2ce0ddd71","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:08:01.000Z","msg":"推(2/10)"},{"pid":"e7c9349ae7112a2d3e0c64fabf914d130569b7e7","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"推(3/10)"},{"pid":"42370b9b3292947ffced0aeef8e7577d6af0eb3c","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"推(4/10)"},{"pid":"bcf0f59283990bd6d26177e3989e7dd60aa7c44b","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"推(5/10)"},{"pid":"69b80eb5e3f8ee04434bcfc7d5b7302056113fd3","tid":1652031,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"推(6/10)"},{"pid":"f0afd80c6538f4e22e9d1bedb31f6f7646